data.description: This beautiful brick ranch is waiting for you to call it home! Over an acre of flat, manicured property delighted with chickpea bushes, fruit trees, and mature oaks. An oversized front porch is perfect to sit and sip coffee. The wrap around drive brings you right up to the back door. Many updates have been made to this home! The unfinished basement is framed and has a fully functioning second bathroom. The possibilities are endless!
